        "userDisplayName": "Bruce Wayne",
        "userUsername": "bwayne",
        "userProfilePic": "https://picsum.photos/200/300?random=3",
        "content": "Totalmente. Un buen diseño elimina la necesidad de justificar decisiones constantemente.",
        "replyToId": 31,
